{#def missing #}
<div class="card bg-base-100 shadow-lg border border-base-300/60">
  <div class="card-body">
    <h2 class="font-display text-xl font-semibold mb-2">
      Here's what we have so far
    </h2>
    <div class="alert alert-warning shadow-sm">
      <span>
        We still don't know {{ missing | join(", ") }}, so we can't
        run a full program screening yet.
      </span>
    </div>
    <p class="text-sm mt-3">
      That's okay &mdash; you can start over any time with a bit more
      detail. And you don't have to wait on us: your local
      <a href="https://www.211.org" target="_blank" rel="noopener"
         class="link link-primary">211 helpline</a>
      (free, 24/7) or mutual aid network can point you toward help
      right away.
    </p>
    <div class="card-actions mt-3">
      <a href="/" class="btn btn-primary btn-sm">Start over with
        more detail</a>
      <a href="https://www.211.org" target="_blank" rel="noopener"
         class="btn btn-outline btn-sm">Go to 211.org</a>
    </div>
  </div>
</div>
